cX1WCKmC0plopqGgn_WXgqHgIg1bXTHqor3fnEY45BR3BxfSv-g6HCoJELKFtlpJeN0282mSIfhPq_cLeSigTcQY4MmXLdE88gN0Ku4GjoY71FlQBBRt_uHUc84-aGToyPhpqEd38A-0DoQl9YIYWy09oX5wcFKPoO58K0jJlBIAdhXkSoGm7-B8rjGEzD1hcOCJpNoVNRgQmSOhXW5pRsCED6WFRQFqOvkwuFiivdoi7K7OIAnxtVp5y08gmeGRGbRuFu5ALUgtDgz-aN1_BXAlq7WOf8EFaM_PO8J9KPzipNCKA8i7vaBwObts-VwTF9Nn03a_xifl6ajL6XkayB935cPykW4pKO6xeK5MRe1M-6ZmFAAtaoQ/8uIuB1Xmi6XJ5BMGlxcb7FCz41DRnJUH/20" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;特朗普在关税和贸易会议后赞扬巴西卢拉&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;周四在白宫的会面是自特朗普贸易战和特朗普盟友、策划针对卢拉的右翼政变的前总统贾尔·博尔索纳罗发生冲突以来两国关系恶化以来的第三次面对面会面。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;三个月后，特朗普在最高法院遭遇罕见的失败&lt;/strong&gt;，导致其贸易战的基础无效，而他最新的征收关税尝试&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ITawXV7sWqf0umXOuRCGzvPzkdgXHEiFtG3yDqXz2a0oNPYEqh8c7QQ39gY5-3IGZl8Cgp7meu4TtLZdRnXefdESCLt4jNKT6oFH6cswK5fFODviTkD6ECaJvtkM1L-JZouNsRmWxbu8Sc-FGbI75XxX02k1ONDCtn25de4HBoE8VK3-meQr1zK0zjYCQqlyGXWyGId4y-b6PMFWjFbEqQ2yiNVFEU45M9ma5sJFz3E61NgwEf8gAijQoU51jQ5feP-QIrMwtuPjwtUSBfmcsg9a7nCxQflEj8j5GEJtGicfvYhyFAkQ70yrS6Q6qQeg2WL_Ks4ak5vM2WExSxSKnyzNk7G6r31qYX9eRla18UVqTfWn7LHzoDDF5Hf0eXYfmnT88lDaRgKktW3OMqYOseoLxTcRCTzdrncssSLwPby9-hHQAcEaNzAGbHLKdmq6n73wOY76j-ZmIYysTI5F2ODcOhFhj6utn-6mZQwT40uxEfx3YLJ_jePPe9lkuGcVU7JeVBKPLJoGdX0S7AAJSf4EYE0/CyXcTByL87p0yIRMe2YvrzpWBrh3RY1C/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国贸易法庭宣布特朗普最新 10% 关税非法"&gt;却遭到了司法打击&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;周四，位于曼哈顿的美国国际贸易法院，一个由三名法官组成的意见分歧的小组推翻了他根据 1974 年《贸易法》第 122 条征收的 10% 关税，该条此前从未被援引过。早期的关税是根据另一部法律《国际紧急经济权力法》颁布的，该法同样从未用于此目的。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;花旗集团在宣传中制定了新的目标&lt;/strong&gt;，以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BisROu-cS0UBZfwWXRLpVK42mjv7N-dtoeCG0AxWAqymVS_OFShh1VirZnqQxqvZnjZ0syHmHIo21nu_zzk4QvwM0VFUUn0JSQWAtcebmIKgsdJg2m9xMGkyBiWPyZ32jrXmOsnOMlkV9ZSQPbt-DsL-8nkbwx-3aIAhiZcBc38EPeGmOyHAwh4AJFgOkv_O7S-ywJHgIzfW_Bq4R9YwfG1MpWtCDrk-4qO2TJA_bB3w4QTf_nE-u824fINubBS1Nv8Fa03fLIZ_TZXyzQ0INBxQs2QVPxEh3sNyS9O6c5f5eYJWa2kw4b2xz5omtqW_Jd5EIpDO8B-3qrdPFE17aLI-9URhJSaJXcS5wK6QbZibswTaVd6rmHzY7Z4DnqdQYFM-_A4eIAMcei49lKh75h025nTwjKd_LdUeBvsSUCg1gcj2B6B2VuNHUNPv6fv5cC7YnVqAOV9nx9G36tirwbsgXjLhFGylMd89FhAb53A8WRikLP3x9AKz-1iYHHVTafCsqs3IT83e4cXopAx-mmebBylLKw/uRbTWHqfKgHobK632mBflviX1SaxF3br/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="花旗向投资者制定新的增长目标"&gt;说服投资者，在多年来努力纠正监管机构的投诉并摆脱落后形象之后，它可以向华尔街竞争对手靠拢&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/emlv1v-0hqb01uSFmiW5_V8A6zwCQIgI5cVY04sSsIUn0FxHVo-fma4EK4T1i3b9cKPKqPUX4ne0oy8aCGDGDUAP0lymw4HZqBVUhL_jPT0d2d9f0qkPwlZfDK3nUTUXheIz6v5T1b_veLtd9VniTAu0eWbdzuphLUJr5iYgu_sk_lWKbu3omhO-RgekyYbzXqKeMz-_ojotAcvtJqfYoQSFvOwbgSVrO3d4ruXBsylFpbYX0zisfIeN8A1-APmOIfTydskPuLeK_28HK2YCVuBPsnkvdm-FuEIwW2oUE_1tZaeJLCkb4zsX2VkBSng4rO-XnnDEV0wqfFpVHDNNub16KXsWzRgoC2qo7eqPdIIJaLtQ0_YHPmshB3VREvH0sKTj0QgXGqTeWk6Lt5xl/cLIoTOUlQ5suII3maonBAuu8Np_OX_lf/20" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJ4nc8vTraS8/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1